snippet: Keith Ratliff, who helped make online videos of high-powered weapons and explosives, was found surrounded by guns, but not the one that killed him.
abstract: Keith Ratliff, Georgia gun enthusiast with popular online videos, is shot to death in Carnesville; officials are treating it as homicide.

byline.contributor: Dan Barry contributed reporting from New York.

lead_paragraph: Keith Ratliff, who helped make online videos of high-powered weapons and explosives, was found surrounded by guns, but not the one that killed him.

headline.seo: Keith Ratliff, Gun Enthusiast of FPSRussia, Is Shot to Death
headline.main: Gun Enthusiast With Popular Online Videos Is Shot to Death in Georgia
